io.github.struppigel.parser

Interface Characteristic

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FileSubtype
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComImageFlag, DebugType, DllCharacteristic, DrvFileSubtype, FileCharacteristic, FileOS, FileType, FontFileSubtype, MachineType, RelocType, SectionCharacteristic, Subsystem, UndefinedSubtype

    public interface Characteristic
    Represents characteristic flags used by the PE format. These include, among others, file characteristics, dll characteristics, subsystem, machinetype, reloctypes.
